    <!-- About Screen -->
    <string name="about_description">UPI Assistant lets you scan UPI QR codes and make payments via USSD (*99#). It also tracks your transaction history, account balances, and automates the USSD payment flow.</string>
    <string name="about_features">• QR scanning\n• Auto-fill USSD payment flow\n• Transaction history and receipts\n• Account balance tracking\n• Missed-call balance check\n• No tracking or analytics</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_note">This application does NOT process payments directly. UPI PIN is stored in memory only and cleared on reboot. Transaction and balance data is stored encrypted on-device. USSD service availability depends on telecom operator and bank support.</string>
